{"tid":2367430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"郭偉強就駕駛期間開視像會議致歉並解釋是偷時間為社區服務","createTime":"2021-01-15T10:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T11:27:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c28e4a1448739cf6713957dedca1134fcd94dcc9","tid":2367430,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:36:01.000Z","msg":"郭偉強就駕駛期間開視像會議致歉 稱會配合任何調查<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員郭偉強昨日被揭發在駕駛期間，參與房屋事務委員會視像會議，他今日就事件致歉，說會深刻反省駕駛態度，承諾日後會嚴格遵守道路交通使用者規例，若日後有任何相關調查及行動，他會配合。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉強昨日參與視像會議期間，以立法會為虛擬背景。他不時左望右望，亦有部份畫面顯示他佩戴安全帶。他昨日在社交網站回應指，天氣寒冷，車上暖氣是他的避寒中心，已盡快在適當位置停車繼續開會；又說「左撲右撲都是為社區服務」，並呼籲大家要注意路上安全。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2374943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2374943&d=ZtPc16BOUua4x2eUEWBZFnXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=9e2e4f98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2374943</a>"},{"pid":"b707faeb760f3b5c7370d8670da1432e275d818d","tid":2367430,"uid":143230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:38:10.000Z","msg":"配合調查-&gt;唔檢控<br />\n當香港人傻"},{"pid":"5402c21cb22348c7739642ec399c001521712b1e","tid":2367430,"uid":278152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562821ce3821a3ff13a92d655814d9798defab23","tid":2367430,"uid":198216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"嚴正執法"},{"pid":"1b7e0cf49b25ead14359d9b2a5f4dd905741d957","tid":2367430,"uid":53687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T10:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https:/